.:: Einstein-puzzle ::.

There are 5 different favourite colors: grey, lilac, chestnut, orange, amber
There are 5 different nationalities: malaysian, american, nigerian, mexican, brazilian
There are 5 different favourite beverages: soy-lemonade, sprite, lemonade, 7up, fanta
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: greymaster, havana, montecristo, baccarat, alhambra
5 different pets are kept: goat, frog, lizard, mouse, hamster
1. the malaysian is the person who likes chestnut
2. the swedish is the owner of the lizard
3. the american is the person drinking 7up
4. the person who likes lilac is on the left of the person who likes orange
5. the person who likes lilac is the person drinking sprite
6. the montecristo-smoker is the owner of the frog
7. the person who likes amber is the havana-smoker
8. the person drinking lemonade is in the middle
9. the mexican is on the far left
10. the alhambra-smoker is on the left or right of the owner of the goat
11. the owner of the hamsters is on the left or right of the havana-smoker
12. the greymaster-smoker is the person drinking soy-lemonade
13. the nigerian is the baccarat-smoker
14. the mexican is on the left or right of the person who likes grey
15. the alhambra-smoker is on the left or right of the person drinking fanta

.:: Answer ::.
|		|	1	|	2	|	3	|	4	|	5	|
| Color		|    amber	|     grey	|      chestnut	|     lilac	|     orange	|
| Nationality	|   mexican	|    american	|    malaysian	|    nigerian	|    swedish	|
| Pet		|     goat	|    hamster	|     frog	|     mouse	|      lizard	|
| Beverage	|    fanta	|     7up	|     lemonade	|    sprite	|      soy-lemonade	|
| Cigar		|   havana	|    alhambra	|  montecristo	|    baccarat	|   greymaster	|
